data.description: Inviting 3-bed, 2-bath that is an off frame modular on concrete and block foundation. Located in a peaceful, quaint setting surrounded by nature. New decking, and crushed coquina sand walkway to add to this home’s appeal. Enjoy the beautiful open floor plan with tasteful paint throughout. Large master bedroom with walk-in closet. Front paver walkway and a 10 x 15 paver back patio! Ideal for nature lovers seeking tranquility. Whole house K water filtration/softener system. You also have a double lofted shed and two car carport. Just 20 minutes from Palm Coast and I-95. Close to Haw creek preserve where you can hike, kayak, and canoe. Also close to dead lake with great fishing and boating. Bring your RV or boat! Experience the serenity of this exceptional property. Schedule your visit today!
